1. @BeforeSuite      ➤ Runs once before everything (e.g., setup DB, reports)
2. @BeforeTest       ➤ Before any <test> in testng.xml
3. @BeforeClass      ➤ Before first method in the current class
4. @BeforeMethod     ➤ Runs before each @Test method
5. @Test             ➤ The actual test case(s)
6. @AfterMethod      ➤ Runs after each @Test method
7. @AfterClass       ➤ After all methods in the current class
8. @AfterTest        ➤ After all  <test> in testng.xml
9. @AfterSuite       ➤ Runs once after everything (cleanup)
